{
  "module": "psspy",
  "function_name": "machine_data",
  "category": "Power Flow Data",
  "description": "This API routine is obsolete. It has been replaced by the API routine machine_data_2, and is implemented by a call to machine_data_2. Use this API to modify the data of an existing machine in the working case or to add a new machine to a plant bus in the working case. This API routine was first introduced in release 28.0.0. ierr = machine_data(ibus, id, intgar, realar)",
